						               													<description>The Lost Island is a treasure hunting game, where you, your family and friends fight and trade among each other to collect many riches and become the most wealthy person.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game includes 10 different game objectives for a fresh new experience every time you play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player will have their own player objective to fulfill before the game ends, and automatically lose if he/she failed to finish it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round, a player picks up an event card, for an exciting beginning either luck or unlucky.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During a player's turn, you have to roll 2 dice and play according to the dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are 5 different actions in the dice &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Force trade&amp;#10;     Movement&amp;#10;     Fight&amp;#10;     Build map&amp;#10;     Go mining &amp;#10;     Your choice of action&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are hidden treasure chests on the map that could help you become wealthy faster. Your goal is to finish your player objective, game objective, and collect as much money as possible by trading cards, fighting your teammates, crafting jewelry, and collecting treasure chests.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
